00:47:54.810 --> 00:47:56.370
than people that
think about it a lot

00:47:56.370 --> 00:47:59.010
and have the tools
to develop the rules

00:47:59.010 --> 00:48:00.060
of the road, the service.

00:48:00.060 --> 00:48:01.380
